<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:14:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>路透调查显示中国4月份新增人民币贷款下降，政策支持到位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-new-yuan-loans-seen-falling-policy-support-place-2024-05-09/</link><description>路透调查显示，尽管央行继续保持对经济的政策支持，但由于季节性因素，中国四月份新增人民币贷款可能较三月份大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 17:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-new-yuan-loans-seen-falling-policy-support-place-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>马杜罗议员之子称委内瑞拉愿意向中国偿还100亿美元债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/venezuela-presidents-son-says-country-is-open-paying-10-billion-debt-china-2024-05-09/</link><description>委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的儿子、议员尼古拉斯·马杜罗·格拉周四在接受路透社采访时表示，委内瑞拉愿意偿还其欠中国的 100 亿美元债务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/venezuela-presidents-son-says-country-is-open-paying-10-billion-debt-china-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>受中国市场打击，菲拉格慕第一季度收入下降 17%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-ferragamo-down-17-first-quarter-2024-05-09/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团 Salvatore Ferragamo 第一季度的收入按固定汇率计算下降了 16.6%，原因是中国市场处境艰难，而且所有地区和渠道的销售普遍放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-ferragamo-down-17-first-quarter-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业因间谍气球事件受到美国贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-administration-adds-37-chinese-entities-trade-restriction-list-2024-05-09/</link><description>拜登政府周四将 37 个中国实体列入贸易限制名单，其中一些实体涉嫌支持去年飞越美国上空的间谍气球，加剧了北京和华盛顿之间的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-administration-adds-37-chinese-entities-trade-restriction-list-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：先进的人工智能模型落入坏人之手会带来哪些风险？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-risks-do-advanced-ai-models-pose-wrong-hands-2024-05-09/</link><description>据路透社周三报道，拜登政府准备开辟一条新战线，努力保护美国人工智能免受中国和俄罗斯的侵害，初步计划在最先进的人工智能模型周围设置护栏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-risks-do-advanced-ai-models-pose-wrong-hands-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国与中国讨论朝鲜问题并表达遣返担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-discusses-north-korea-with-china-airs-repatriation-concerns-2024-05-09/</link><description>美国国务院表示，负责朝鲜问题的美国高级官员周四在东京与中国官员讨论了该问题，并对中国强行遣返朝鲜人表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-discusses-north-korea-with-china-airs-repatriation-concerns-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>印度应亲华领导人要求完成从马尔代夫撤军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-completes-troop-exit-maldives-pro-china-leaders-request-2024-05-09/</link><description>新德里官员周四表示，在总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖的要求下，印度已用平民取代了马尔代夫的约 80 名士兵，穆伊祖已将马尔代夫的关系转向中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 14:49:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-completes-troop-exit-maldives-pro-china-leaders-request-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>Coach母公司Tapestry因美国和中国需求不温不火而下调销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coach-parent-tapestry-misses-quarterly-revenue-expectations-2024-05-09/</link><description>Coach 手袋制造商 Tapestry 周四下调了年度销售预期，并且未达到第三季度收入预期，这表明北美和中国对其手提包和配饰的需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coach-parent-tapestry-misses-quarterly-revenue-expectations-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国贸易升温，英国利率值得关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:30:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国对美国人工智能技术的依赖程度如何？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/how-dependent-is-china-us-artificial-intelligence-technology-2024-05-09/</link><description>据路透社报道，拜登政府计划对美国开发的人工智能（AI）模型设置护栏，这些模型为 ChatGPT 等流行聊天机器人提供支持，以保护该技术免受中国和俄罗斯等国家的侵害。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/how-dependent-is-china-us-artificial-intelligence-technology-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>高管表示，中国比亚迪将考虑于 2025 年在欧洲建立第二家工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-will-consider-second-european-plant-2025executive-says-2024-05-09/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪欧洲董事总经理迈克尔舒周四表示，该公司将考虑于 2025 年在欧洲建设第二家组装厂。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-will-consider-second-european-plant-2025executive-says-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦警方称，枪手在瓜达尔港附近杀害了七名劳工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gunmen-pakistan-kill-seven-labourers-near-gwadar-port-say-police-2024-05-09/</link><description>警方称，周四早些时候，枪手在巴基斯坦西南部瓜达尔港附近枪杀了七名工人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:41:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/gunmen-pakistan-kill-seven-labourers-near-gwadar-port-say-police-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国取代中国成为德国最大贸易伙伴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-overtakes-china-germanys-top-trading-partner-2024-05-09/</link><description>路透社根据德国统计局官方数据计算得出，今年第一季度，美国超过中国，成为德国最重要的贸易伙伴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-overtakes-china-germanys-top-trading-partner-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>在美国的担忧下，中国军舰计划访问柬埔寨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-warships-plan-visit-cambodia-amid-us-worries-2024-05-09/</link><description>中国国防部表示，中国将从5月上半月到6月中旬向柬埔寨和东帝汶派遣两艘军舰，这可能会进一步令美国对中国在柬埔寨一个重要海军基地的存在日益增加感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 06:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-warships-plan-visit-cambodia-amid-us-worries-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国碧桂园计划在下周之前支付错过的优惠券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-says-it-aims-pay-onshore-coupons-due-thursday-by-may-13-2024-05-09/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商碧桂园表示，无法支付周四到期的两张境内息票，但如果未能在下周结束的宽限期内支付，中债保险公司将代其支付。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 04:59:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-says-it-aims-pay-onshore-coupons-due-thursday-by-may-13-2024-05-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>